function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorDonan) then -- delete old fake donan
		Hydra.ActorDelete(actorDonan)
	end

	--get relevant references from trigger
	locDonan = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "locDonan")[1]
	gizmoDonanBook = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Book")[1]
	fakeDonan = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "fakeDonan")[1]
	actorDonanFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(donanFollowerSNO)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(fakeDonan)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorDonanFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorDonanFollower, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(actorDonanFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorDonanFollower, locDonan, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)

		Hydra.QActorDelete(actorDonanFollower)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorDonanFollower)
	end
	
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convChat_01, fakeDonan)
	Hydra.QActorAnim(fakeDonan, animKeyDonanMagicBook)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(gizmoDonanBook)
	
end
